 <h2>
  Research Interest
 </h2>
 <p>
  My research interests, in a broad sense, include networked control systems, decentralized/distributed algorithm design for multi-agent systems, nonlinear control theory and robotics. Detailed information is avalible at
  <a href="SolmazKia_CV-2017.pdf">
   my CV.
  </a>
 </p>
 <h2>
  Current Open Positions
 </h2>
 <p>
  <b>
   PhD (Fall 2019)
  </b>
  - There are two Ph.D. openings in my lab in Fall 2019 (If interested, please apply directly to the MAE department and I will review your application during the review process. You can list me as UCI correspondence. I apologize, but I do not typically respond to email inquiries due to the large number of the recieved emails. However, I read all the emails and keep a copy of the attached CVs.)
  <br/>
  <b>
   Post-Doc
  </b>
  - Cooperative localization for mobil agents
  <br/>
  <b>
   Post-Doc
  </b>
  - Cooeprative persistent montoring via mobile agents
 </p>
